readme:
GeoMap:

  Created on 2020-05-03T19:37:32Z

  The geomap dictionary contains information about the 
  lithology, stratigraphy, and a combining descriptor,
  which can be used as legends. The main convenience of
  this format is the included list of polygons which 
  each contain the aforementioned descriptors, 
  lithological, and stratigraphical information needed 
  to be used as legends Each Polygon contains info for
  one single geological region/feature.

  Features included in his map:

  o  Continental or island arc slope, except Antarctica
